&lt;li&gt;S. in Engineering, Computer Science or similar technical field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical and problem-solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work with export-controlled technology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
